{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, I was just asked to go and shoot this film called \"Elizabeth.\""},{"time":3000,"text":"And we're all talking about this great English icon and saying,"},{"time":6000,"text":"\"She's a fantastic woman, she does everything."},{"time":8000,"text":"How are we going to introduce her?\""},{"time":10000,"text":"So we went around the table with the studio and the producers and the writer,"},{"time":12000,"text":"and they came to me and said, \"Shekhar, what do you think?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"And I said, \"I think she's dancing.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"And I could see everybody looked at me,"},{"time":20000,"text":"somebody said, \"Bollywood.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"The other said, \"How much did we hire him for?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"And the third said, \"Let's find another director.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"I thought I had better change."},{"time":29000,"text":"So we had a lot of discussion on how to introduce Elizabeth,"},{"time":31000,"text":"and I said, \"OK, maybe I am too Bollywood."},{"time":34000,"text":"Maybe Elizabeth, this great icon, dancing?"},{"time":36000,"text":"What are you talking about?\""},{"time":38000,"text":"So I rethought the whole thing,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and then we all came to a consensus."},{"time":42000,"text":"And here was the introduction of this"},{"time":44000,"text":"great British icon called \"Elizabeth.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"Leicester: May I join you, my lady?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"Elizabeth: If it please you, sir."},{"time":66000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"Shekhar Kapur: So she was dancing."},{"time":112000,"text":"So how many people who saw the film did not get"},{"time":115000,"text":"that here was a woman in love,"},{"time":117000,"text":"that she was completely innocent"},{"time":119000,"text":"and saw great joy in her life, and she was youthful?"},{"time":122000,"text":"And how many of you did not get that?"},{"time":126000,"text":"That's the power of visual storytelling,"},{"time":128000,"text":"that's the power of dance, that's the power of music:"},{"time":131000,"text":"the power of not knowing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"When I go out to direct a film,"},{"time":136000,"text":"every day we prepare too much, we think too much."},{"time":138000,"text":"Knowledge becomes a weight upon wisdom."},{"time":141000,"text":"You know, simple words lost"},{"time":143000,"text":"in the quicksand of experience."},{"time":147000,"text":"So I come up, and I say,"},{"time":149000,"text":"\"What am I going to do today?\" I'm not going to do what I planned to do,"},{"time":152000,"text":"and I put myself into absolute panic."},{"time":155000,"text":"It's my one way of getting rid of my mind,"},{"time":158000,"text":"getting rid of this mind that says,"},{"time":160000,"text":"\"Hey, you know what you're doing. You know exactly what you're doing."},{"time":162000,"text":"You're a director, you've done it for years.\""},{"time":164000,"text":"So I've got to get there"},{"time":166000,"text":"and be in complete panic."},{"time":168000,"text":"It's a symbolic gesture. I tear up the script,"},{"time":170000,"text":"I go and I panic myself, I get scared."},{"time":173000,"text":"I'm doing it right now; you can watch me. I'm getting nervous,"},{"time":176000,"text":"I don't know what to say, I don't know what I'm doing, I don't want to go there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"And as I go there, of course, my A.D. says,"},{"time":181000,"text":"\"You know what you're going to do, sir.\" I say, \"Of course I do.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"And the studio executives, they would say,"},{"time":187000,"text":"\"Hey, look at Shekhar. He's so prepared.\""},{"time":189000,"text":"And inside I've just been listening to Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan"},{"time":191000,"text":"because he's chaotic."},{"time":193000,"text":"I'm allowing myself to go into chaos"},{"time":196000,"text":"because out of chaos, I'm hoping some moments of truth will come."},{"time":200000,"text":"All preparation is preparation."},{"time":202000,"text":"I don't even know if it's honest."},{"time":204000,"text":"I don't even know if it's truthful."},{"time":206000,"text":"The truth of it all comes on the moment, organically,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and if you get five great moments"},{"time":211000,"text":"of great, organic stuff"},{"time":213000,"text":"in your storytelling, in your film,"},{"time":215000,"text":"your film, audiences will get it."},{"time":217000,"text":"So I'm looking for those moments, and I'm standing there"},{"time":219000,"text":"and saying, \"I don't know what to say.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"So, ultimately, everybody's looking at you,"},{"time":223000,"text":"200 people at seven in the morning"},{"time":225000,"text":"who got there at quarter to seven, and you arrived at seven,"},{"time":227000,"text":"and everybody's saying,"},{"time":229000,"text":"\"Hey. What's the first thing? What's going to happen?\""},{"time":231000,"text":"And you put yourself into a state of panic"},{"time":233000,"text":"where you don't know, and so you don't know."},{"time":236000,"text":"And so, because you don't know,"},{"time":238000,"text":"you're praying to the universe because you're praying to the universe"},{"time":241000,"text":"that something -- I'm going to try and access the universe"},{"time":244000,"text":"the way Einstein -- say a prayer --"},{"time":246000,"text":"accessed his equations,"},{"time":248000,"text":"the same source. I'm looking for the same source"},{"time":251000,"text":"because creativity comes from absolutely the same source"},{"time":253000,"text":"that you meditate somewhere outside yourself,"},{"time":255000,"text":"outside the universe."},{"time":257000,"text":"You're looking for something that comes and hits you."},{"time":259000,"text":"Until that hits you, you're not going to do the first shot."},{"time":261000,"text":"So what do you do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"So Cate says, \"Shekhar, what do you want me to do?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"And I say, \"Cate, what do you want to do?\" (Laughter)"},{"time":268000,"text":"\"You're a great actor, and I like to give to my actors --"},{"time":271000,"text":"why don't you show me what you want to do?\""},{"time":273000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":275000,"text":"What am I doing? I'm trying to buy time."},{"time":277000,"text":"I'm trying to buy time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"So the first thing about storytelling that I learned,"},{"time":281000,"text":"and I follow all the time is: Panic."},{"time":283000,"text":"Panic is the great access of creativity"},{"time":286000,"text":"because that's the only way to get rid of your mind."},{"time":288000,"text":"Get rid of your mind."},{"time":290000,"text":"Get out of it, get it out."},{"time":292000,"text":"And let's go to the universe because"},{"time":294000,"text":"there's something out there that is more"},{"time":296000,"text":"truthful than your mind,"},{"time":298000,"text":"that is more truthful than your universe."},{"time":300000,"text":"[unclear], you said that yesterday. I'm just repeating it"},{"time":302000,"text":"because that's what I follow constantly"},{"time":304000,"text":"to find the shunyata somewhere, the emptiness."},{"time":307000,"text":"Out of the emptiness comes a moment of creativity."},{"time":310000,"text":"So that's what I do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312000,"text":"When I was a kid -- I was about eight years old."},{"time":314000,"text":"You remember how India was. There was no pollution."},{"time":317000,"text":"In Delhi, we used to live -- we used to call it a chhat or the khota."},{"time":321000,"text":"Khota's now become a bad word. It means their terrace --"},{"time":324000,"text":"and we used to sleep out at night."},{"time":326000,"text":"At school I was being just taught about physics,"},{"time":328000,"text":"and I was told that"},{"time":331000,"text":"if there is something that exists,"},{"time":333000,"text":"then it is measurable."},{"time":336000,"text":"If it is not measurable,"},{"time":338000,"text":"it does not exist."},{"time":340000,"text":"And at night I would lie out, looking at the unpolluted sky,"},{"time":343000,"text":"as Delhi used to be at that time when I was a kid,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and I used to stare at the universe and say,"},{"time":349000,"text":"\"How far does this universe go?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"My father was a doctor."},{"time":353000,"text":"And I would think, \"Daddy, how far does the universe go?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"And he said, \"Son, it goes on forever.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"So I said, \"Please measure forever"},{"time":362000,"text":"because in school they're teaching me"},{"time":364000,"text":"that if I cannot measure it, it does not exist."},{"time":367000,"text":"It doesn't come into my frame of reference.\""},{"time":370000,"text":"So, how far does eternity go?"},{"time":372000,"text":"What does forever mean?"},{"time":374000,"text":"And I would lie there crying at night"},{"time":377000,"text":"because my imagination could not touch creativity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"So what did I do?"},{"time":382000,"text":"At that time, at the tender age of seven,"},{"time":384000,"text":"I created a story."},{"time":386000,"text":"What was my story?"},{"time":388000,"text":"And I don't know why, but I remember the story."},{"time":391000,"text":"There was a woodcutter"},{"time":393000,"text":"who's about to take his ax and chop a piece of wood,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and the whole galaxy is one atom of that ax."},{"time":401000,"text":"And when that ax hits that piece of wood,"},{"time":404000,"text":"that's when everything will destroy"},{"time":406000,"text":"and the Big Bang will happen again."},{"time":408000,"text":"But all before that there was a woodcutter."},{"time":410000,"text":"And then when I would run out of that story,"},{"time":412000,"text":"I would imagine that woodcutter's universe"},{"time":415000,"text":"is one atom in the ax of another woodcutter."},{"time":418000,"text":"So every time, I could tell my story again and again"},{"time":421000,"text":"and get over this problem,"},{"time":423000,"text":"and so I got over the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426000,"text":"How did I do it? Tell a story."},{"time":429000,"text":"So what is a story?"},{"time":431000,"text":"A story is our -- all of us --"},{"time":434000,"text":"we are the stories we tell ourselves."},{"time":437000,"text":"In this universe, and this existence,"},{"time":441000,"text":"where we live with this duality"},{"time":443000,"text":"of whether we exist or not"},{"time":445000,"text":"and who are we,"},{"time":447000,"text":"the stories we tell ourselves are the stories"},{"time":450000,"text":"that define the potentialities"},{"time":452000,"text":"of our existence."},{"time":454000,"text":"We are the stories we tell ourselves."},{"time":459000,"text":"So that's as wide as we look at stories."},{"time":461000,"text":"A story is the relationship"},{"time":463000,"text":"that you develop between who you are,"},{"time":467000,"text":"or who you potentially are,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and the infinite world, and that's our mythology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"We tell our stories,"},{"time":475000,"text":"and a person without a story does not exist."},{"time":478000,"text":"So Einstein told a story"},{"time":481000,"text":"and followed his stories and came up with theories"},{"time":484000,"text":"and came up with theories and then came up with his equations."},{"time":487000,"text":"Alexander had a story that his mother used to tell him,"},{"time":490000,"text":"and he went out to conquer the world."},{"time":492000,"text":"We all, everybody, has a story that they follow."},{"time":495000,"text":"We tell ourselves stories."},{"time":497000,"text":"So, I will go further, and I say,"},{"time":500000,"text":"\"I tell a story, and therefore I exist.\""},{"time":502000,"text":"I exist because there are stories,"},{"time":504000,"text":"and if there are no stories, we don't exist."},{"time":506000,"text":"We create stories to define our existence."},{"time":509000,"text":"If we do not create the stories,"},{"time":511000,"text":"we probably go mad."},{"time":514000,"text":"I don't know; I'm not sure, but that's what I've done all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517000,"text":"Now, a film."},{"time":521000,"text":"A film tells a story."},{"time":523000,"text":"I often wonder when I make a film -- I'm thinking of making a film of the Buddha --"},{"time":526000,"text":"and I often wonder: If Buddha had all the elements"},{"time":530000,"text":"that are given to a director --"},{"time":532000,"text":"if he had music, if he had visuals, if he had a video camera --"},{"time":535000,"text":"would we get Buddhism better?"},{"time":537000,"text":"But that puts some kind of burden on me."},{"time":539000,"text":"I have to tell a story"},{"time":541000,"text":"in a much more elaborate way,"},{"time":543000,"text":"but I have the potential."},{"time":545000,"text":"It's called subtext."},{"time":547000,"text":"When I first went to Hollywood, they said --"},{"time":549000,"text":"I used to talk about subtext, and my agent came to me,"},{"time":551000,"text":"\"Would you kindly not talk about subtext?\""},{"time":554000,"text":"And I said, \"Why?\" He said, \"Because nobody is going to give you a film"},{"time":556000,"text":"if you talk about subtext."},{"time":559000,"text":"Just talk about plot"},{"time":561000,"text":"and say how wonderful you'll shoot the film,"},{"time":563000,"text":"what the visuals will be.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":565000,"text":"So when I look at a film,"},{"time":567000,"text":"here's what we look for:"},{"time":569000,"text":"We look for a story on the plot level,"},{"time":572000,"text":"then we look for a story"},{"time":574000,"text":"on the psychological level,"},{"time":576000,"text":"then we look for a story on the political level,"},{"time":579000,"text":"then we look at a story"},{"time":581000,"text":"on a mythological level."},{"time":583000,"text":"And I look for stories on each level."},{"time":585000,"text":"Now, it is not necessary"},{"time":587000,"text":"that these stories agree with each other."},{"time":590000,"text":"What is wonderful is,"},{"time":592000,"text":"at many times, the stories will contradict with each other."},{"time":596000,"text":"So when I work with Rahman who's a great musician,"},{"time":598000,"text":"I often tell him, \"Don't follow what the script already says."},{"time":602000,"text":"Find that which is not."},{"time":604000,"text":"Find the truth for yourself,"},{"time":606000,"text":"and when you find the truth for yourself,"},{"time":608000,"text":"there will be a truth in it, but it may contradict the plot,"},{"time":610000,"text":"but don't worry about it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"So, the sequel to \"Elizabeth,\" \"Golden Age.\""},{"time":617000,"text":"When I made the sequel to \"Elizabeth,\" here was a story that"},{"time":619000,"text":"the writer was telling:"},{"time":621000,"text":"A woman who was threatened"},{"time":624000,"text":"by Philip II"},{"time":626000,"text":"and was going to war,"},{"time":628000,"text":"and was going to war, fell in love with Walter Raleigh."},{"time":630000,"text":"Because she fell in love with Walter Raleigh,"},{"time":633000,"text":"she was giving up the reasons she was a queen,"},{"time":635000,"text":"and then Walter Raleigh"},{"time":637000,"text":"fell in love with her lady in waiting,"},{"time":639000,"text":"and she had to decide whether she was a queen going to war"},{"time":641000,"text":"or she wanted..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"Here's the story I was telling:"},{"time":648000,"text":"The gods up there,"},{"time":650000,"text":"there were two people."},{"time":652000,"text":"There was Philip II, who was divine"},{"time":655000,"text":"because he was always praying,"},{"time":658000,"text":"and there was Elizabeth, who was divine,"},{"time":660000,"text":"but not quite divine because she thought she was divine,"},{"time":662000,"text":"but the blood of being mortal flowed in her."},{"time":665000,"text":"But the divine one was unjust,"},{"time":668000,"text":"so the gods said,"},{"time":670000,"text":"\"OK, what we need to do is"},{"time":672000,"text":"help the just one.\""},{"time":675000,"text":"And so they helped the just one."},{"time":677000,"text":"And what they did was, they sent Walter Raleigh down"},{"time":680000,"text":"to physically separate her mortal self"},{"time":683000,"text":"from her spirit self."},{"time":685000,"text":"And the mortal self was the girl"},{"time":687000,"text":"that Walter Raleigh was sent,"},{"time":689000,"text":"and gradually he separated her"},{"time":692000,"text":"so she was free to be divine."},{"time":694000,"text":"And the two divine people fought,"},{"time":696000,"text":"and the gods were on the side of divinity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":698000,"text":"Of course, all the British press got really upset."},{"time":702000,"text":"They said, \"We won the Armada.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"But I said, \"But the storm won the Armada."},{"time":707000,"text":"The gods sent the storm.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"So what was I doing?"},{"time":711000,"text":"I was trying to find a mythic reason"},{"time":713000,"text":"to make the film."},{"time":715000,"text":"Of course, when I asked Cate Blanchett, I said, \"What's the film about?\""},{"time":718000,"text":"She said, \"The film's about a woman"},{"time":720000,"text":"coming to terms with growing older.\""},{"time":723000,"text":"Psychological."},{"time":725000,"text":"The writer said \"It's about history, plot.\""},{"time":728000,"text":"I said \"It's about mythology,"},{"time":730000,"text":"the gods.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"So let me show you a film --"},{"time":734000,"text":"a piece from that film --"},{"time":736000,"text":"and how a camera also --"},{"time":738000,"text":"so this is a scene, where in my mind,"},{"time":740000,"text":"she was at the depths of mortality."},{"time":743000,"text":"She was discovering what mortality actually means,"},{"time":746000,"text":"and if she is at the depths of mortality,"},{"time":749000,"text":"what really happens."},{"time":751000,"text":"And she's recognizing the dangers of mortality"},{"time":753000,"text":"and why she should break away from mortality."},{"time":756000,"text":"Remember, in the film, to me,"},{"time":758000,"text":"both her and her lady in waiting"},{"time":760000,"text":"were parts of the same body,"},{"time":762000,"text":"one the mortal self"},{"time":764000,"text":"and one the spirit self."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767000,"text":"So can we have that second?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":769000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":771000,"text":"Elizabeth: Bess?"},{"time":775000,"text":"Bess?"},{"time":778000,"text":"Bess Throckmorton?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":785000,"text":"Bess: Here, my lady."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"Elizabeth: Tell me, is it true?"},{"time":789000,"text":"Are you with child?"},{"time":793000,"text":"Are you with child?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"Bess: Yes, my lady."}]},{"cues":[{"time":797000,"text":"Elizabeth: Traitorous."},{"time":800000,"text":"You dare to keep secrets from me?"},{"time":802000,"text":"You ask my permission before you rut,"},{"time":805000,"text":"before you breed."},{"time":807000,"text":"My bitches wear my collars."},{"time":809000,"text":"Do you hear me? Do you hear me?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":811000,"text":"Walsingham: Majesty. Please, dignity. Mercy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814000,"text":"Elizabeth: This is no time for mercy, Walsingham."},{"time":817000,"text":"You go to your traitor brother and leave me to my business."},{"time":820000,"text":"Is it his?"},{"time":822000,"text":"Tell me. Say it. Is the child his? Is it his?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"Bess: Yes."},{"time":827000,"text":"My lady,"},{"time":829000,"text":"it is my husband's child."},{"time":834000,"text":"Elizabeth: Bitch! (Cries)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837000,"text":"Raleigh: Majesty."},{"time":839000,"text":"This is not the queen I love and serve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":847000,"text":"Elizabeth: This man has seduced a ward of the queen,"},{"time":850000,"text":"and she has married without royal consent."},{"time":854000,"text":"These offenses are punishable by law. Arrest him."},{"time":858000,"text":"Go."},{"time":864000,"text":"You no longer have the queen's protection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":868000,"text":"Bess: As you wish, Majesty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"Elizabeth: Get out! Get out! Get out!"},{"time":878000,"text":"Get out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"Shekhar Kapur: So, what am I trying to do here?"},{"time":905000,"text":"Elizabeth has realized,"},{"time":907000,"text":"and she's coming face-to-face"},{"time":909000,"text":"with her own sense of jealousy,"},{"time":911000,"text":"her own sense of mortality."},{"time":913000,"text":"What am I doing with the architecture?"},{"time":916000,"text":"The architecture is telling a story."},{"time":918000,"text":"The architecture is telling a story"},{"time":920000,"text":"about how, even though she's the most powerful woman"},{"time":922000,"text":"in the world at that time,"},{"time":924000,"text":"there is the other, the architecture's bigger."},{"time":928000,"text":"The stone is bigger than her because stone is an organic."},{"time":930000,"text":"It'll survive her."},{"time":932000,"text":"So it's telling you, to me, stone is part of her destiny."},{"time":936000,"text":"Not only that, why is the camera looking down?"},{"time":939000,"text":"The camera's looking down at her because she's in the well."},{"time":942000,"text":"She's in the absolute well"},{"time":944000,"text":"of her own sense of being mortal."},{"time":947000,"text":"That's where she has to pull herself out"},{"time":950000,"text":"from the depths of mortality,"},{"time":952000,"text":"come in, release her spirit."},{"time":954000,"text":"And that's the moment where, in my mind,"},{"time":956000,"text":"both Elizabeth and Bess are the same person."},{"time":959000,"text":"But that's the moment"},{"time":961000,"text":"she's surgically removing herself from that."},{"time":964000,"text":"So the film is operating on"},{"time":966000,"text":"many many levels in that scene."},{"time":968000,"text":"And how we tell stories"},{"time":970000,"text":"visually, with music, with actors,"},{"time":973000,"text":"and at each level it's a different sense"},{"time":975000,"text":"and sometimes contradictory to each other."},{"time":979000,"text":"So how do I start all this?"},{"time":984000,"text":"What's the process of telling a story?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"About ten years ago,"},{"time":989000,"text":"I heard this little thing from a politician,"},{"time":992000,"text":"not a politician that was very well respected in India."},{"time":995000,"text":"And he said that these people in the cities,"},{"time":998000,"text":"in one flush, expend as much water"},{"time":1002000,"text":"as you people in the rural areas"},{"time":1004000,"text":"don't get for your family for two days."},{"time":1007000,"text":"That struck a chord, and I said, \"That's true.\""},{"time":1010000,"text":"I went to see a friend of mine,"},{"time":1012000,"text":"and he made me wait"},{"time":1014000,"text":"in his apartment in Malabar Hill"},{"time":1016000,"text":"on the twentieth floor,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"which is a really, really upmarket area in Mumbai."},{"time":1020000,"text":"And he was having a shower for 20 minutes."},{"time":1022000,"text":"I got bored and left, and as I drove out,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"I drove past the slums of Bombay,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"as you always do,"},{"time":1028000,"text":"and I saw lines and lines in the hot midday sun"},{"time":1030000,"text":"of women and children with buckets"},{"time":1033000,"text":"waiting for a tanker"},{"time":1035000,"text":"to come and give them water."},{"time":1037000,"text":"And an idea started to develop."},{"time":1039000,"text":"So how does that become a story?"},{"time":1041000,"text":"I suddenly realized that we are heading towards disaster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1044000,"text":"So my next film is called \"Paani\""},{"time":1046000,"text":"which means water."},{"time":1048000,"text":"And now, out of the mythology of that,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"I'm starting to create a world."},{"time":1052000,"text":"What kind of world do I create,"},{"time":1054000,"text":"and where does the idea, the design of that come?"},{"time":1057000,"text":"So, in my mind, in the future,"},{"time":1059000,"text":"they started to build flyovers."},{"time":1062000,"text":"You understand flyovers? Yeah?"},{"time":1064000,"text":"They started to build flyovers"},{"time":1066000,"text":"to get from A to B faster,"},{"time":1068000,"text":"but they effectively went from one area of relative wealth"},{"time":1071000,"text":"to another area of relative wealth."},{"time":1073000,"text":"And then what they did was"},{"time":1075000,"text":"they created a city above the flyovers."},{"time":1077000,"text":"And the rich people moved to the upper city"},{"time":1080000,"text":"and left the poorer people in the lower cities,"},{"time":1083000,"text":"about 10 to 12 percent of the people"},{"time":1086000,"text":"have moved to the upper city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1088000,"text":"Now, where does this upper city and lower city come?"},{"time":1090000,"text":"There's a mythology in India about --"},{"time":1092000,"text":"where they say, and I'll say it in Hindi,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"[Hindi]"},{"time":1099000,"text":"Right. What does that mean?"},{"time":1101000,"text":"It says that the rich are always sitting on the shoulders"},{"time":1104000,"text":"and survive on the shoulders of the poor."},{"time":1106000,"text":"So, from that mythology, the upper city and lower city come."},{"time":1108000,"text":"So the design has a story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111000,"text":"And now, what happens is that the people of the upper city,"},{"time":1114000,"text":"they suck up all the water."},{"time":1116000,"text":"Remember the word I said, suck up."},{"time":1118000,"text":"They suck up all the water, keep to themselves,"},{"time":1120000,"text":"and they drip feed the lower city."},{"time":1122000,"text":"And if there's any revolution, they cut off the water."},{"time":1124000,"text":"And, because democracy still exists,"},{"time":1127000,"text":"there's a democratic way in which you say"},{"time":1130000,"text":"\"Well, if you give us what [we want], we'll give you water.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1133000,"text":"So, okay my time is up."},{"time":1135000,"text":"But I can go on about telling you"},{"time":1137000,"text":"how we evolve stories,"},{"time":1139000,"text":"and how stories effectively are who we are"},{"time":1142000,"text":"and how these get translated into the particular discipline"},{"time":1144000,"text":"that I am in, which is film."},{"time":1146000,"text":"But ultimately, what is a story? It's a contradiction."},{"time":1149000,"text":"Everything's a contradiction."},{"time":1151000,"text":"The universe is a contradiction."},{"time":1153000,"text":"And all of us are constantly looking for harmony."},{"time":1155000,"text":"When you get up, the night and day is a contradiction."},{"time":1157000,"text":"But you get up at 4 a.m."},{"time":1159000,"text":"That first blush of blue is where the night and day"},{"time":1161000,"text":"are trying to find harmony with each other."},{"time":1164000,"text":"Harmony is the notes that Mozart didn't give you,"},{"time":1167000,"text":"but somehow the contradiction of his notes suggest that."},{"time":1169000,"text":"All contradictions of his notes suggest the harmony."},{"time":1173000,"text":"It's the effect of looking for harmony"},{"time":1175000,"text":"in the contradiction that exists in a poet's mind,"},{"time":1178000,"text":"a contradiction that exists in a storyteller's mind."},{"time":1181000,"text":"In a storyteller's mind, it's a contradiction of moralities."},{"time":1184000,"text":"In a poet's mind, it's a conflict of words,"},{"time":1186000,"text":"in the universe's mind, between day and night."},{"time":1189000,"text":"In the mind of a man and a woman,"},{"time":1191000,"text":"we're looking constantly at"},{"time":1193000,"text":"the contradiction between male and female,"},{"time":1195000,"text":"we're looking for harmony within each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1197000,"text":"The whole idea of contradiction,"},{"time":1200000,"text":"but the acceptance of contradiction"},{"time":1203000,"text":"is the telling of a story, not the resolution."},{"time":1205000,"text":"The problem with a lot of the storytelling in Hollywood"},{"time":1207000,"text":"and many films, and as [unclear] was saying in his,"},{"time":1210000,"text":"that we try to resolve the contradiction."},{"time":1213000,"text":"Harmony is not resolution."},{"time":1215000,"text":"Harmony is the suggestion of a thing"},{"time":1217000,"text":"that is much larger than resolution."},{"time":1219000,"text":"Harmony is the suggestion of something"},{"time":1221000,"text":"that is embracing and universal"},{"time":1224000,"text":"and of eternity and of the moment."},{"time":1226000,"text":"Resolution is something that is far more limited."},{"time":1230000,"text":"It is finite; harmony is infinite."},{"time":1233000,"text":"So that storytelling, like all other contradictions in the universe,"},{"time":1236000,"text":"is looking for harmony and infinity"},{"time":1239000,"text":"in moral resolutions, resolving one, but letting another go,"},{"time":1242000,"text":"letting another go and creating a question that is really important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1246000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1248000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}